CoreBox v2.2
================

These are the some big changes in CoreBox 2.2.

=> CoreBox
   - Added new app CoreTerminal, CoreRenamer, CorePDF and CoreArchiver.
   - Removed engrampa as moved to CoreArchiver
   - Reduced font size in all app's sidebar.
   - Fixed tab close crash of same app.
   - Full trash support for CoreFM and CoreImage.
   - Moved window buttons to sidebar and fixed the DobuleClick to window maximize.
   - Added new Dark and light mode.
   - Redesigned all the ui and sidebar color.
   - Set font style across all the apps.

=> Start
   - New look.
   - Redesigned RecentActivites.
   - Added new feature called save session.

=> BookMarks
    - BookmarkIt Dialog in dark ui.

=> DashBoard
    - Updated the battery info functions.
    - Moved all core code to separate library.
    - Battery charging and discharging time is showing now.
    - Updated the libcsys library.
    - General page's network bar now show used network.

=> Search
   - Search is now faster and have better UI.
   - Keyboard "Enter" shortcut is now working.
   - Added search activity to save the search words.
   - Auto fill the folder path and name from search activity.

=> Settings
   - Now it is possible to backup settings and bookmarks as an archive.

=> CoreAction
   - All the widgets rebuild, now those are faster and ram efficient.
   - Widgets list is now customizable.
   - Redesigned.

=> CoreFM
   - Added drive list.
   - Added full trash support.
   - Added CoreArchiver and CoreTerminal support.
   - Dark ui in corefm.
   - Added Send To option.
   - Removed libmagic from dependency.
   - Added full integration with new apps.
   - Getting file size is faster now.

=> CorePaint
   - Selected area delete with del key press.
   - Moved toolsize in status bar.
   - Added all the instrument cursor.
   - Minor ui changes.

=> CoreTime
   - No new fixes

=> CoreImage
   - Fixed the thumbnail view.

=> CorePlayer
   - Fixed autoPlay problem.

=> CorePDF
   - New app.

=> CorePad
   - Fixed linenumberwidth.
   - Fixed all bug related to saving.
   - Added syntax highlighting.

=> CoreTerminal
   - New app
   - Added copy past option.

=> CoreArchiver
   - New app.
   - Added dark ui.

=> CoreShot
   - Added active window screenshot
   - A new way to capture screenshot.

=> CoreRenamer
    - New app.

=> Tested
    - Manjaro xfce.
    - Ubuntu 18.04 LTS.
    - Qt toolkit version 5.9 lts and 5.11.1
